  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/981020/extras/f6ac2e782f438ef8602c247c0242a235.avif?t=1737936880\" width=600 height=220 /></span><br><br>Mum and Dad have been experimenting on Chaos Servants, but now, the monsters have been let loose. Clea, with her brother in tow, must escape from the Whitlock Mansion.<br><br>Watch your back, Clea. Those closest to you may be the real terror.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/981020/extras/de00f9a2cf546f01c2b23369aa5416cf.poster.avif?t=1737936880\" width=626 height=258 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/981020/extras/de00f9a2cf546f01c2b23369aa5416cf.webm?t=1737936880\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/981020/extras/de00f9a2cf546f01c2b23369aa5416cf.mp4?t=1737936880\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Skill-focused horror:</h2><br>Clea is primarily a test of skills. Enemies roam the halls dynamically in real-time, reacting to the players' every noise. Clea is a challenging title, rewarding those who have mastered its mechanics.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Outwit the Chaos Servants:</h2><br>The Chaos Servants are on the hunt. Listen for their footsteps, peek under doors, and stay far, far away.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/981020/extras/7dbd429668c72af171dce8c78d15e42c.poster.avif?t=1737936880\" width=626 height=258 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/981020/extras/7dbd429668c72af171dce8c78d15e42c.webm?t=1737936880\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/981020/extras/7dbd429668c72af171dce8c78d15e42c.mp4?t=1737936880\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Escape the Whitlock Mansion:</h2><br>The Whitlock family has trapped Clea inside the mansion. Hunt down key items and solve the puzzles designed to lock you from the outside world.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >No jump scares:</h2><br>No prescripted scares, promise. Your skills and actions will determine Clea's fate.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/981020/extras/48c3396df21b2b632c362af688115317.poster.avif?t=1737936880\" width=626 height=258 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/981020/extras/48c3396df21b2b632c362af688115317.webm?t=1737936880\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/981020/extras/48c3396df21b2b632c362af688115317.mp4?t=1737936880\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Unveil family history:</h2><br>The Whitlock bloodline is filled with dark memories. Obtain memory orbs and uncover your family secrets through bonus chapters.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Voice cast:</h2><br>Clea – Xanthe Huynh, Edmond – Anairis Quinones, Florine, Mum – Aimee Smith, Dad – Miguel Moran, Maids – Angela Tran",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/981020/extras/f6ac2e782f438ef8602c247c0242a235.avif?t=1737936880\" width=600 height=220 /></span><br><br>Mum and Dad have been experimenting on Chaos Servants, but now, the monsters have been let loose. Clea, with her brother in tow, must escape from the Whitlock Mansion.<br><br>Watch your back, Clea. Those closest to you may be the real terror.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/981020/extras/de00f9a2cf546f01c2b23369aa5416cf.poster.avif?t=1737936880\" width=626 height=258 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/981020/extras/de00f9a2cf546f01c2b23369aa5416cf.webm?t=1737936880\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/981020/extras/de00f9a2cf546f01c2b23369aa5416cf.mp4?t=1737936880\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Skill-focused horror:</h2><br>Clea is primarily a test of skills. Enemies roam the halls dynamically in real-time, reacting to the players' every noise. Clea is a challenging title, rewarding those who have mastered its mechanics.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Outwit the Chaos Servants:</h2><br>The Chaos Servants are on the hunt. Listen for their footsteps, peek under doors, and stay far, far away.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/981020/extras/7dbd429668c72af171dce8c78d15e42c.poster.avif?t=1737936880\" width=626 height=258 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/981020/extras/7dbd429668c72af171dce8c78d15e42c.webm?t=1737936880\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.